product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"微服务架构，将原本需要大团队，大人力维护的服务，拆分成了一个个模块化的独立小服务。我理解这些服务与对应业务的结合会更紧密，这也能够更加适应业务的发展。以feature team的方式把开发 测试 产品 设计聚合在一起，我认为是与微服务架构拆分的一种有机结合，而不是微服务架构的组成部分，不知道这种理解是否恰当？","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":418444,"discussion_content":"嗯，以团队和业务领域为边界拆分微服务，目标是团队自治+并行开发+快速响应业务需求。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1527611206,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":5625,"user_name":"王宁","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1048061,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4E6258270B7BE9","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/fd/fd/1e3d14ee.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1523657873,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":1836,"content":"理解正确👍","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"杨波","uid":1030344,"ctime":1524747897,"ip_address":"","comment_id":5625,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":4,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"一般来说传统的架构是面向管理和过程控制的。\n微服务是面向产品交付的。虽然传统最终也面向交付，不过这和个架构更加更多是从上到下的管理方式，随着环境和基础设施的完善，现在团队有了更大的自主权和能力来保障交付了。\n\n当然微服务对单个成员要求能力更强了，之前可能说为了满足考核而工作，结果是由老大负责。现在是每个人都要为自己的交付物负责。","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1030344,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","nickname":"杨波","note":"","ucode":"FA3418BB703BCA","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":416796,"discussion_content":"理解正确👍","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1524747897,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":38706,"user_name":"张闯","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1090513,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D5AD46A8DD6FB7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a3/d1/a30a4d06.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1542111084,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":4,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"微服务架构本质上是一种组织架构的重组。\n这里说的重组，应该是指从按照职能（技术技能）来组织团队转变为按照产品（特性）来组织团队的过程。\n职能团队将关注点主要放在技术上，团队成员掌握了同一个技术知识。\n跨职能的特性团队将关注点放在业务和产品上，团队成员掌握了同一个产品特性的知识。\n由于，团队间的沟通成本远大于团队内的沟通成本。因此，要将沟通频率更高的问题和沟通价值更高的问题放到团队内部。\n由于业务是不断变化的。所以，相比于技术问题，业务问题是沟通频率更高的问题。\n由于对于大部分企业来说，真正产生价值的是公司的主营业务，而非公司积累的技术专利。所以，相比于技术问题，业务问题是沟通价值更高的问题。\n因此，以业务关注点来划分特性团队，相比于以技术关注来划分职能团队，会让整个企业内部的沟通效率更高，让企业更具市场竞争力。","like_count":33,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1205697,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/65/c1/afcd981b.jpg","nickname":"程序员二师兄","note":"","ucode":"C9E3B5B3358BDF","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":177352,"discussion_content":"讲的真好","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1582097364,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":2176,"user_name":"jimmy","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1003262,"ip_address":"","ucode":"F7CC7E298AD0C8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/4e/fe/2f5d1bb7.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1516165354,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":4,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"架构是演化出来的，开始要保证simple原则，尽可能简单","like_count":15},{"had_liked":false,"id":2258,"user_name":"jch","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1046536,"ip_address":"","ucode":"828A5D81761E4F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/f8/08/3ebc9864.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1516520927,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":4,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"微服务的团队更加专注于某类业务，迭代服务的开发。而传统的开发团队所有业务都接触，难以专注","like_count":9},{"had_liked":false,"id":2423,"user_name":"ancestor","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1048233,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4CC58D51EAC8B0","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/fe/a9/38389926.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1517152644,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":4,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"分情况，有的场景下：架构是设计出来的；而有的时候是需要不断演进而来的","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":2191,"user_name":"梅子黄时雨","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1015938,"ip_address":"","ucode":"9F788D09C2E9E7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/80/82/3c21b30c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1516251833,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":4,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"把原先按照职能来划分的组织打散，重新按照契合微服务的开发方式来组织。比如，原先甲属于研发团队，后来微服务来了，其中有个用户微服务，安排甲来做微服务，那甲就属于用户微服务团队了。","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":38493,"user_name":"珠闪闪","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1300447,"ip_address":"","ucode":"45BE0D586A3839","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/DYAIOgq83eov38ZkwCyNoBdr5drgX0cp2eOGCv7ibkhUIqCvcnFk8FyUIS6K4gHXIXh0fu7TB67jaictdDlic4OwQ/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1542067406,"is_pvip":false,"repli